CODE:
Program
Comments
Toggling of p1.5 with the delay of 5ms without interrupts using timer 1
ORG 0000H
MOV TMOD, #10h
AGAIN: MOV TL1, #0FFH
MOV TH1, #0EDH
CPL P1.5
SETB TR1
BACK: JNB TF1, BACK
CLR TR1
CLR TF1
SJMP AGAIN
END
