Load Timer 1 registers with the desired delay value
Toggle P1.5 by completing the current state
Set Timer 1 Run bit
Continuously check the Timer 1 Overflow
Clearing the Timer run(Stop the timer)
Clearing the Overflow(for the next timer cycle))
Repeat the entire process
